name: COLIN JOST GOT MARRIED. COLIN JUST GOT MARRIED.
description: File this one under absurd fiddle-faddle. Colin Jost, is an American comedian, actor, and writer famous for his work on 'Saturday Night Live'. He married actress Scarlett Johansson in 2020. So, here we have some facts. 1. Colin Jost got married. 2. Colin JUST (as in recently) got married. Both of these sentences are true and all we did was change one letter. Both are referring to the same person doing the same thing, yet in completely separate instances. Pretty fascinating when you think about it. Can you come up with a sentence like this? Try it...
